		<span class="navoption"><a href="#" onclick="contactMode()">Contact</a></span>
	</div>
	<div class="main">
		<table><tr><td>
			<div style="background-color:#208A08;">
			<div style="text-align:center;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;color:#208A08;font-size:14pt;background-color:#ffffff;border:2px solid #208A08;border-bottom:none;max-width:100%;padding: 9px 12px 9px 12px;">
				Who can use this map?
			</div>
			<button class="focusGroup" onmouseover="illustrate(0)" onclick="toMap(0)">
				<span style="color:#ffffff;">Stranger on the Street</span><br/>
				<blockquote>
					<ul><li>"I saw this computer in a coffee shop..."</li></ul>
				</blockquote>
				<blockquote>
					<ul><li>"What are students and teachers doing with the XO?"</li></ul>
				</blockquote>
			</button>
			<br/>
			<button class="focusGroup" onmouseover="illustrate(1)" onclick="toMap(1)">
				<span style="color:#ffffff;">Potential Volunteer</span><br/>
				<blockquote>
					<ul><li>"I know a school in India which would love this..."</ul></li>
				</blockquote>
				<blockquote>
					<ul><li>"Where can I buy an XO for my program?"</ul></li>
				</blockquote>				
			</button>
			<br/>
			<button class="focusGroup" onmouseover="illustrate(2)" onclick="toMap(2)">
				<span style="color:#ffffff;">The OLPC Classroom</span><br/>
				<blockquote>
					<ul><li>"Can you help me fix my XO and add more classroom activities?"</ul></li>
				</blockquote>
				<blockquote>
					<ul><li>"How can I find penpals and volunteers worldwide?"</ul></li>
				</blockquote>
			</button>
			</div>
		</td><td>
			<img src="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/bigmap.jpg" style="min-width:600px;width:100%;" class="stretch" alt=""/>
			<div style="background: transparent url(http://mapmeld.appspot.com/frontpagemap.jpg);">
				<div id="infoBubble" style="position:absolute;left:550px;top:220px;text-align:center;width:320px;">
					<!--<img src=""/>-->
					<div id="infoBubbleContent" style="background-color:#ffffff;padding-left:12px;padding-right:12px;padding-top:8px;">
						<a id="mapLink" href="http://olpcMAP.net/map?q=Mongolia">
							<img id="infoBubbleImg" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3003/2916377218_5b140df150_m.jpg" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/olpc/4900464912/" width="300" height="210" alt="OLPC"/>
						</a>
						<br/>
						<img src="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/cc-by.jpg" style="height:9pt;vertical-align:middle;"/> OLPC Flickr
					</div>
					<img src="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/bottomQ.png" style="width:100%;"/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</td></tr></table>
